rification.","breadcrumbs":[{"label":"Connecticut"}],"sections":[{"label":"CT Service Areas","heading":"Cities We Serve in Connecticut","body":"Our dedicated teams provide consistent, verifiable cleaning services throughout Connecticut. Select a city below to learn about our services in your area.","features":["Stamford — Fairfield County: Full commercial janitorial, disinfection, floor care, and facility maintenance services.","Bridgeport — Fairfield County: Full commercial janitorial, disinfection, floor care, and facility maintenance services.","New Haven — New Haven County: Full commercial janitorial, disinfection, floor care, and facility maintenance services.","Hartford — Hartford County: Full commercial janitorial, disinfection, floor care, and facility maintenance services.","Norwalk — Fairfield County: Full commercial janitorial, disinfection, floor care, and facility maintenance services.","Danbury — Fairfield County: Full commercial janitorial, disinfection, floor care, and facility maintenance services.","Waterbury — New Haven County: Full commercial janitorial, disinfection, floor care, and facility maintenance services.","Greenwich — Fairfield County: Full commercial janitorial, disinfection, floor care, and facility maintenance services."]},{"heading":"Industries We Serve in Connecticut","body":"We specialize in six core verticals across Connecticut, each with dedicated cleaning protocols designed for its specific compliance and safety requirements.","features":["Schools & Educational Facilities: CDC-compliant cleaning for K-12 schools, charter schools, private academies, and universities.","Churches & Houses of Worship: Respectful, meticulous cleaning for sanctuaries, fellowship halls, nurseries, and administrative offices for congregations of all sizes.","Healthcare & Medical Offices: OSHA-compliant terminal cleaning for medical offices, dental practices, outpatient clinics, urgent care centers, and long-term care facilities.","Daycare & Childcare C